{"tid":1427743,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老閪都唔割席，不過機場黎講","createTime":"2019-08-07T07:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T12:39:41.000Z","uid":212646,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"08aea9db3f440ff696f3e7fabd2164f42a76483e","tid":1427743,"uid":212646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:34:17.000Z","msg":"如果衝嘅話係可以去到國際恐襲級別<br />\n當然係睇你點衝<br />\n除咗雞場特犬，仲可能有國際間嘅制裁<br />\n但唔同一般攬炒<br />\n因為到時已經唔係俾人label做暴徒咁簡單<br />\n而係恐怖分子<br />\nInterpol都可以出手的<br />\n如果真係有人衝，只要手足三思而行，我一定唔割席，但希望大家少心到時身邊有鬼，我會建議和理非"},{"pid":"96113472b90c20b3a54053e812304071963eacea","tid":1427743,"uid":212646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:37:13.000Z","msg":"總有人想扣帽子話我係三毛<br />\n但我真係希望每個去機場嘅手足都諗清楚"},{"pid":"4982326de98d16d312086fa85a578320d74ccf21","tid":1427743,"uid":212646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:43:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70eb2d02cfb6c426861ecaca35e981bf6f1ae469","tid":1427743,"uid":212646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:46:23.000Z","msg":"絶不割席"},{"pid":"3076b3f5f2e79bc66cafa72e74c0d811811d00de","tid":1427743,"uid":266683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T12:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AeSVOga.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAeSVOga.png&h=77554cf2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0LukZnR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0LukZnR.png&h=464a8fb6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pddRmBb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpddRmBb.png&h=41338f5e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sToJW9x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsToJW9x.jpg&h=c24dac2e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}